has an important message that
I'm anxious for you to hear.

36:32.440 --> 36:34.608
Rachel, I'm sorry.
I'm gonna have to stop you.

36:36.319 --> 36:40.155
The way you've been acting
is totally inappropriate.

36:40.240 --> 36:43.325
I'm your teacher, Rachel.
And I'm sorry, but that's
all I'm ever gonna be.

36:45.203 --> 36:47.454
I know.

36:48.623 --> 36:51.959
I— I brought
these for you
as an apology.

36:53.962 --> 36:56.088
And the song
I was gonna sing was...

36:56.172 --> 36:58.465
